==English==
===Etymology===
A pormanteau coined by ''Tiger Woods'' to describe his ethnic makeup. ''Ca'' for [[Caucasian]], ''bl'' for [[black]], ''in'' for [[American Indian]] and ''asian'' for [[Asian]] (namely [[Thai]]).

====Pronunciation====
ca'*blin*'asian:

===Adjective===
'''cablinasian'''
#Of mixed [[descent]].

===Noun===
'''cablinasian'''
# A person of cablinasian descent